      "description": "This is a good, honest car that presents well and should make a solid driver for someone who wants something enjoyable and usable without paying top-dollar for a show car. It appears to have been kept up reasonably well, with a clean overall presentation and the kind of normal age-related wear you\u2019d expect on a vehicle that has been used and cared for over time. Buyers can expect a car that looks respectable, feels above average, and should suit someone looking for a nice example with some minor imperfections rather than a fully restored or flawless one.",
