    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Older used car in poor condition and priced accordingly. This is not a clean, turnkey vehicle \u2014 expect noticeable cosmetic wear, a tired overall presentation, and the likelihood that it will need repairs and ongoing attention. Best suited for someone looking for a budget project, basic transportation with realistic expectations, or possibly a parts car depending on their needs. If you want something polished or trouble-free, this probably is not the right fit, but for the right buyer it could still be a usable low-cost option.",
