    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer seeking dependable basic transportation or a solid project platform. It shows its age and wear, but presents an honest value with plenty of potential for the right owner. Priced to move and ideal for someone who appreciates a low-entry-cost option with room to make it their own.",
