      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not a showpiece and could use some TLC, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone needing simple transport, a first project, or a handy spare vehicle. Priced to sell and worth a look if you want something affordable without any fuss.",
