    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid mechanical bones and plenty of life left for the next owner. Engine pulls clean, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis feels composed enough to serve as an affordable daily, project, or backup vehicle. It shows cosmetic age and wear consistent with a well-used car, but the fundamentals are there: dependable startup, usable powerband, and a platform that still has good utility. If you want inexpensive transportation with character and decent road manners, this one is worth a look.",
